As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 642 people, 299 households, and 175 families residing in the city.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2020: Coleman city, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Coleman+city;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

